					 MOVE 0  TO KEY-CODE-1
					 MOVE 1  TO KEY-TYPE
					 GO TO BA35
				     END-IF
				 END-IF
		 WHEN ENTER-KEY  GO TO BA40
		 WHEN OTHER	 CALL X"E5"
	       END-EVALUATE
